'''Iron Ore''' is obtained from Iron [[Mining#Mining Nodes|nodes]] with a [[Pickaxes|pickaxe]]. Mining an Iron Node will yield between 1 and 3 Iron Ore. The [[Skills#Mining|Miner Profession]] can further increase this.

==Locations==
* [[The Mines]] (Floors 41 - 79) have a high concentration of [[Mining#Mining Nodes|Iron Nodes]] with potential abundance at Floors 71 - 79.
* Nodes can spawn in the [[Quarry]], the [[Quarry Mine]], or in the quarry on the [[Farm Maps|Hill-top and Four-Corners Farm Maps]]
* Can be found in breakable crates and barrels in [[The Mines]]
* Can be bought at the [[Blacksmith]] for {{price|150}} each in year 1 and for {{price|250}} each in year 2+
* Can be found at any Floor of the [[Skull Cavern]]
* Can be dropped by [[Metal Head]]s in Floors 80-119 of [[The Mines]], by [[Stone Golem]]s, by [[Dust Sprite]]s, or by [[Slimes|Iron Slimes]].
* Can be found in [[Fishing#Treasure Chests|Fishing Treasure Chests]]
* Can be found by [[Hoes|tilling]] soil in [[The Mines]]
* Can be found inside any of the 4 types of [[Minerals#Geodes|Geode]]
* Can be found by [[Copper Pan|panning]]
* Occasionally sold by the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|10}}
* Can be found in [[Garbage Can]]s.
* Can be [[Recycling Machine|recycled]] from [[Trash (item)|Trash]] with a 21% chance.
* An [[Ice Pip]] [[Fish Pond]] can produce 5 Iron Ore when the population of the pond reaches 3.

==Smelting==
Iron ore can be smelted in a [[Furnace]] to create an [[Iron Bar]]. The smelting requires 5 iron ore and 1 [[coal]] to begin and takes 2 in-game hours to complete.

