==Tailoring==
Iron Ore can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring|Turtleneck Sweater]].  [[File:Shirt178.png|24px]]

==Quests==
Ten Iron Ore are requested by [[Ice Pip]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 1 to 3.

==History==
{{History|1.3.27|Increased price at the [[Blacksmith]] from 150g in year 1 to 250g in year 2+.}}
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]]. Can be requested in a Fish Pond quest. Can be produced by Fish Ponds.}}

